Package Appointment

Class AppointmentService

java.lang.Object
Appointment.DoctorAvailabilityService
Appointment.AppointmentService
All Implemented Interfaces:
AppointmentManager, DoctorAvailabilityManager
public class AppointmentService extends DoctorAvailabilityService implements AppointmentManager
The AppointmentService class provides functionality for managing appointments, including scheduling, rescheduling, canceling, and viewing appointment statuses. It extends the DoctorAvailabilityService and implements the AppointmentManager interface.
